You are building a Zoom Marketplace App. Follow these rules:

1. Use @zoom/appssdk for all Zoom SDK interactions
2. Call zoomSdk.config() before any API calls
3. Use the OAuth proxy URL: https://zoomvibes.j4red4llen.com/api/oauth/proxy/start?provider=zoom
4. NEVER expose Client Secret in client-side code
5. Use Zoom's color scheme: Primary #0E71EB, Light bg #FFFFFF, Dark bg #242424
6. Design for embedded mode with compact layouts (280-400px width)
7. Handle both light and dark themes

The template includes:
- src/lib/zoom.ts - SDK initialization utilities
- src/hooks/useZoom.ts - React hook for Zoom SDK
- src/components/ZoomApp.tsx - Main app component

Start by customizing ZoomApp.tsx for your use case.
